    "created_at": "2016-10-24T07:14:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-10-24T07:14:38Z",
    "body": "When passing an extra callback, the call becomes asynchronous and macOS assumes that the app is still able to to other tasks, so it doesn't disable the menu items automatically.\n"
